{
  "name": "RPlog_Dark_Wedding",
  "title": "Dark Wedding",
  "summary": "Aboard the Predator, in a shadowed ritual chamber dedicated to the Caspian god Olum, Captain Antoine Dareus weds Serenella Jordain in a dark handfasting ceremony presided over by the high priest Axel. Inanna escorts her sister Serenella, the bride, into the candlelit room alongside the quiet Sarian woman Lila, while Dareus stands nervously before his assembled officers. Axel rings the welcome bell, binds the couple's clasped hands around an obsidian dagger with a silver cord, and lights candles invoking Olum's blessings of understanding, strength, desire, and fulfillment. In place of spoken vows Serenella sings a tender love song, and Dareus answers with a heartfelt pledge to remain by her side until his last breath. Axel completes the rite by drawing the dagger to cut both their palms and catch their mingled blood in a chalice, sealing their souls with fire before pronouncing them husband and wife, after which the wedding party departs to celebrate.",
